description:
&lt;h1&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Bank Facilities Assistants - WE WANT YOU!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span&gt;Various shift patterns available &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We cover the whole Integrated Care Organisation which includes Torbay, Newton Abbot, Totnes and Brixham Hospitals, Paignton, Teignmouth &amp; Ashburton Wellbeing Hubs and will include the cleaning of our nursing homes should the need arise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Covering 7 days a week including Saturdays, Sundays and Bank holidays&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These shifts may fit around another job, College/University and work life balance. &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Facilities Department are looking for dedicated people to join the team of Facilities - Hotel Services. The successful candidates will be required to ensure the required cleanliness of designated areas to National Cleaning Standards. And the control and prevention of infection control.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role includes cleaning clinical areas, ward areas, public areas and office areas, including COVID areas.  Also the delivery and preparation of food and drinks to the patients, ordering of meals from catering and kitchen duties regarding HACCP.  Mandatory and localized training will be carried out via E-Learning and shadowing in the role.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&lt;strong&gt;(For all the above applicants should be able to demonstrate good literacy and numeracy skills, be able to work well in a team or on their own, be capable of undertaking physical work on a daily basis and have experience of working with nursing teams &amp; the general public). &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In return for your hard work and your professional, caring and reliable service we offer:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Competitive pay&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Paid annual leave&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Access to the NHS pension scheme&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Free training and development opportunities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Experience gained by working on various wards across the Acute Hospital and Community Hospitals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
